interpretation: The shark emoji represents power, dominance, and aggression. It symbolizes a force to be reckoned with, and a predator in its natural habitat. The shark reminds us to assert ourselves and take charge, using our strength and instincts to overcome any obstacles in our way. It can also signify danger and a need to be cautious in our surroundings. The shark card encourages us to tap into our primal nature and trust our gut instincts, while also being aware of potential threats and navigating them with confidence. Some associated keywords include: strength, dominance, aggression, power, danger, instinct, survival, resilience, confidence, and assertiveness.
